<collectingCountry id="F34CFDCF1D0C2B55595FFA1C73DC5733" box="[1125,1216,1519,1543]" name="Thailand" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Thailand</collectingCountry>
and Peninsular 
<collectingCountry id="F34CFDCF1D0C2B55585FFA1C72DA5733" box="[1381,1478,1519,1543]" name="Malaysia" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C341EED41D0C2B555E50F9E473FB57DB" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE4BD5F1D0C2B555E50F9E473FB57DB" blockId="17.[828,1480,1559,1775]" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B555E50F9E474E6571B" box="[874,1018,1559,1583]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Observations</emphasis>
. – This species is morphologically similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C5BC6DC1D0C2B555E6DF9C474DE577B" box="[855,962,1591,1615]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B555E6DF9C474DE577B" box="[855,962,1591,1615]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">B. humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but lacks the tesselate venation and armed pleats on the leaves that characterized the latter. Furthermore, 
<taxonomicName id="4C5BC6DC1D0C2B5558B8F9A472DC575B" box="[1410,1472,1623,1647]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="toei">
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B5558B8F9A472DC575B" box="[1410,1472,1623,1647]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">B.toei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a syncarp with fewer and smaller drupes (160 drupes of 
<quantity id="4CA310BA1D0C2B555E06F96474B4579B" box="[828,936,1687,1711]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.65" metricValueMax="1.8" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" unit="mm" value="16.5" valueMax="18.0" valueMin="15.0">15-18 mm</quantity>
longvs 240-430 drupes of 
<quantity id="4CA310BA1D0C2B5559FCF964722E579B" box="[1222,1330,1687,1711]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="2.5" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" unit="mm" value="22.5" valueMax="25.0" valueMin="20.0">20-25 mmin</quantity>
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B555875F96472A6579B" box="[1359,1466,1687,1711]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">
<taxonomicName id="4C5BC6DC1D0C2B555875F96472AE579B" box="[1359,1458,1687,1711]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">B.humilis</taxonomicName>
)
</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C5BC6DC1D0C2B555E06F94474C357FB" box="[828,991,1719,1743]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Benstonea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="toei">
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B555E06F94474C357FB" box="[828,991,1719,1743]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Benstonea toei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was strangely omitted from 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCAC0AE1D0C2B555826F94472DA57FB" author="STONE, B. C." box="[1308,1478,1719,1743]" journalOrPublisher="Fed. Mus. J." pageId="17" pageNumber="340" pagination="1 - 74" part="23" refId="ref16436" refString="STONE, B. C. (1978). Revisio Pandanacearum, Part I. Pandanus subgenera Coronata and Acrostigma. Flora Malesiana precursores. Fed. Mus. J. 23: 1 - 74." title="Revisio Pandanacearum, Part I. Pandanus subgenera Coronata and Acrostigma. Flora Malesiana precursores" type="journal article" year="1978">STONE’ s (1978)</bibRefCitation>
revision of 
<taxonomicName id="4C5BC6DC1D0C2B555E8FF92473FC57DB" box="[949,1248,1751,1775]" class="Liliopsida" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Pandanus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pandanales" pageId="17" pageNumber="340" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Acrostigma">
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B555E8FF924733C57DB" box="[949,1056,1751,1775]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Pandanus</emphasis>
subg. 
<emphasis id="B92F614D1D0C2B55595CF92473FC57DB" box="[1126,1248,1751,1775]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="340">Acrostigma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
